WEBVTT

00:01.167 --> 00:02.862
<i>NARRATOR: Previously on</i> One Tree Hill.

00:02.936 --> 00:04.460
I'm not here to talk about Jamie.

00:04.537 --> 00:06.971
I'd just always wondered
if he knows who I am.

00:07.040 --> 00:08.564
He found a picture of you once.

00:08.641 --> 00:10.836
- What'd you tell him?
- I told him you were dead.

00:11.177 --> 00:13.407
It's Mia. She's the magic, Peyton.

00:13.480 --> 00:17.541
And I'm telling you, her spark is
getting squashed by this ass of a singer.

00:17.617 --> 00:20.142
Oh, this is for you.
It's supposed to bring good luck.

00:21.021 --> 00:24.889
I know we just met, but I just wanted
you to know that I'm here.

00:24.958 --> 00:26.152
Good to know.

00:26.226 --> 00:29.662
Any student who walks out
that door fails this quarter.

00:29.729 --> 00:33.028
Say goodbye to extracurricular
activities, say goodbye to sports.

00:33.099 --> 00:34.361
Like basketball.

